{"tid":127840,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"「遇著擋路　穿插巴士站上停留」","createTime":"2017-02-20T11:18:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-21T08:41:00.000Z","uid":72532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5935bad27865144653b4ae99cb20989eefe8f5f1","tid":127840,"uid":72532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T11:18:17.000Z","msg":"早前巴士司機慘遭票控指未埋站就上落客，<br />\n自此之後按章依法辦事，應記一功。<br />\n呢單案嘅重點唔係有無殺人，<br />\n而係浪子回頭金不換。<br />\n<br />\n依法巴士<br />\n#Jeep #陳柏宇 #陳詠謙 #溫翰文<br />\n<br />\n遇著擋路　穿插巴士站上停留<br />\n不上落客　煞掣為了依法　未泊到站頭<br />\n<br />\n站在隊列　趕上班　緊著眉頭<br />\n於正面有個廢老　提著指尖起哄<br />\n規章可有　藏在眼眸<br />\n<br />\n#自信最緊要<br />\n#黃柏喬經典語錄"},{"pid":"c4640eed49714bf4e38fb64b348aabe7b06c5522","tid":127840,"uid":30377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T11:20:41.000Z","msg":"睇到我1999"},{"pid":"38e97a9745aeecc9766f56908235014dc45f03ce","tid":127840,"uid":72532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T11:23:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇到我1999</blockquote><br />\n抱謙小弟唔識用匪語"},{"pid":"f1ec0584a56ffa3ecaf368800259185322a00fe6","tid":127840,"uid":72532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T11:25:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faa5eef14e758df770d98d492763b5faa047fed8","tid":127840,"uid":72532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T11:30:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"498c01ab1c4d6d701ebdb4151ba5ca3626fd3373","tid":127840,"uid":72532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T11:31:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇到我1999</blockquote><br />\n抱謙小弟唔識用匪語</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">歉</span>"},{"pid":"ca50f3ef3aea1e2cd9d7eb31a989ab3c80df233b","tid":127840,"uid":72532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T12:29:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif